Sentencas: B -site double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-delta (SFMMG) is reported as a promising fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: The SFMMG material shows excellent structural stability in both oxidizing and reducing atmospheres, possesses an appropriate thermal expansion coefficient, as well as excellent redox cycle stability.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: The result confirms that the Mg2+ and Ga3+ tend to occupy the B -site while some Fe ions moves to the B'-site, creating lots of FeB-O-FeB' anti -site defects in the lattice.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: As a result, a high electrical conductivity value of 36.0 S cm(-1) is obtained at 800 C-degrees in H-2.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: Besides, the SFMMG electrode exhibits good catalytic activity toward hydrogen oxidation/evolution reaction, as confirmed by the low polarization resistance of 0.237 Omega cm(2) at 800 C-degrees in H-2.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: With SFMMG as the fuel electrode, the La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta (300 mu m) -supported single cell exhibits a peak power density of 1073 mW cm(- 2) in fuel cell mode and an electrolysis current density of 1192 mA
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: cm( -2) in electrolysis cell mode at 900 C.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell

Sentencas: In addition, the single cell shows stable performance during 100 h operation under 0.75 V at 800 C-degrees.
Titulo: Double perovskite Sr2FeMo0.6Mg0.25Ga0.15O6-δ as high-performance fuel electrode for reversible solid oxide cell
